data-triple-N3.o: "Featherston is a town in the north of the Wellington Region of New Zealand. It lies in the Wairarapa, just north of the Rimutaka Tunnel, in the South Wairarapa District. The population was 2,340 in the 2006 Census. The town is on the eastern side of the Rimutaka Range close to the northern shore of Lake Wairarapa. It is 37km south-west of Masterton and 63km north-east of Wellington."@en
